Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是否還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  為了還清總額一億五千萬的債務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也為了保護凪大小姐而戰鬥著的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾崎颯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這種無所謂的事情就暫且丟在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回就讓我們盡情地無視原作和時間空間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏天的沙灘舉行泳裝大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺必死殺必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺必死殺必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺必死殺必死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（EVA預告中三石每次都會說的台詞）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱天很夏  泳裝篇！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:50.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此處標題刻意改變了語序：正確的語序為ナツがアツいぜ(夏天很熱)）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:54.50,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：一；校對：无爱的飞鱼、遠ぃ風；時間：黑羽侖人；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真氣派
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像在南方的小島上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這宅邸裡面  居然還有這樣的私人沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  還有這麼完美的游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這裡是練馬區  實在讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒什麼大不了的  總共才花了幾百億而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那邊的椰子樹每十棵也就才值一億五千萬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一億五千萬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就和我欠的錢一樣多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種破地方究竟有什麼好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是老爺子自己的特殊嗜好而建起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  難得有這樣的沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由不游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯  人在水裡是浮不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯  小凪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來大小姐是旱鴨子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！人本來就是陸生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人的身體構造是不可能在水中生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教您游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛…既然小颯都說到這份上了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就趕快換上泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳…泳衣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等…等等  難道是要我穿泳衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…泳衣的話  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說還太早了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之  我是絕對不會去游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  就憑那種水中專用型還想贏主角機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（眾多的Gundam主角們都削過水中專用型的人棍…最近的貌似就是刹那了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人以泳裝相對 這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  小凪這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐生這麼大的氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是哪裡又做錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯  接下來就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可好啊  小凪  哈亞太君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來玩的～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是被硬拉來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  聽說小凪願意「免費」請我們去游泳池玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把大家叫來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有說過那種話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經為大家準備好各種泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選一件自己喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大的沙灘  不用的話也是浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪  不介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是絕對不會去游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞小姐  這樣真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然交給桂老師去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正如老師所說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起游得很高興的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪也會想一起游的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小颯也選一件怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常適合你呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞小姐  別耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個桂老師居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我之前誤解她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你會遵守約定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在這裡喝酒喝到爽是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您盡情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  大家今天盡情地喝…呃不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地游泳吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌Show  大家已經準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在  Let's  go！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  從剛才開始就在拍些什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我覺得剛才的鏡頭很有記錄的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對我們動畫研究部來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不可錯過的鏡頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這泳衣  感覺布料相當少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主  聽好了  絕對不可以看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  亙  臉怎麼那麼紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  腳踏兩船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你個色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  喜歡哪個多點？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主…下流！無恥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亙  你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不是的  不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  果然什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  亙真H！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲夜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…你們兩個誤會我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…只是被咲夜問到哪個比較喜歡  然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  大家都玩得很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞這種大賤賣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低級的賣肉往往會意外導致人氣的急劇下降哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  不過我覺得這樣很健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道不  牧村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣與學生小鬼們交流  也是咱當老師的很重要的工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白不？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  受教了  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為替上帝引導這些孩子們的指路人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也十分贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理解咱說的話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  滿上  滿上～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是個路過的修女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（假面騎士DECADE：我只不過是個路過的假面騎士）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～雖說也有若干例外啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐也去和大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊  那只不過是小鬼級別的玩法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起跟他們一起胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看某動畫公司的股票狂跌的樣子要有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:17.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（GONZO公司股票已於090401被摘牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  其實還是很在意的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書都拿反了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這是故意的…故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做大腦體操
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta…Tareraya…Renoo…Oogu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有興趣的話 小颯也一起來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…不過把大小姐一個人丟在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係的  你們兩個想去的話就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也能自娛自樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來準備把「豹頭戰士的冒險繪卷」一天內看完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一天之內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯這個笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才似乎感覺到有一股邪氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時  在豪宅門口站著的某位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那個被硬拽上巨大機器人的少年一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大家都聽出來是吐嘈「碇真嗣」了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  姐姐又給大家添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛？我現在在小凪家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家玩得很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  在姐姐繼續添麻煩之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把她帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我這是第一次來小颯住的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是在緊張什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是來接走姐姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊  又不是特意跑來見小颯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是在商店街抽獎抽中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流河免費入場卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我一起被沖走…好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:51.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（雕像捏自1970年大阪世博會雕像「太陽塔」）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  小颯會答應一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛菊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是哈亞太君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我們為對手  居然還能一直贏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然僅靠泉一個人是無法與之抗衡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你們兩個也給我認真點打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好接著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯你這叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白野威
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你是來安慰我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世態炎涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭喲  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐你不是還有我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們都打算背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲份到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意小凪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是大小姐還真是固執啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也差不多該屈服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  怎麼樣了？差不多該…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛歌小姐  千櫻小姐  對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這還真是意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾崎君居然是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就說我是變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  一點都不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:30.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Japnica弱點薄：捏自Fate/hollow ataraxia中的「ジャプニカ暗殺帳」\N實為影射「ジャポニカ学習帳」——日本一系列專為小學生而設的筆記用本）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子已經下狠心了  明明超在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之  對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳  沒想到居然在那種地方換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛…雛菊小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個  我其實不想看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:13:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小颯  那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說我的裸體沒有一點看的價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  又要被雛菊小姐討厭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  原本是想和小颯拉近距離的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又對他發脾氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這泳衣是不是太大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  連這種程度都做不到的話怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少能引起小颯的注意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西澤同學比想像中要成熟得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起可以叫你「Honey」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那樣的話  我也可以叫小颯作…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…西澤同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小颯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須快點找到大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  總算找到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯你非要一起游泳  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小颯  剛才那是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…能不能當作沒發生過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的事就當作沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯你這花心大蘿蔔！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙希  你…怎麼突然弄成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少主…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是班長紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的活躍度可真是超越預期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多虧了泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的文化祭一定會很成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說那種悠閒話的場合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  那不是小凪  她是被什麼東西給附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是把這個小女孩的負面感情化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨靈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…很完美的登場解說詞  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把大小姐的身體還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小女孩和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我生前也…也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去海邊和游泳池游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  一直以來因為幼兒體形感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒穿過一次泳衣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨  好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些賣弄身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來取悅男人們的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些一邊喊著難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊暗自開心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨那些不理解動畫製作的難處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不動就晃動胸部的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份恨意  不覺得應當發洩出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是個沒氣量的怨靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…或者說  完全是在曲解別人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小女孩也和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥著被朋友排斥而產生的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙  比預料中要難對付呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  終於輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（EVA初號機登場！看樣子凪家是第三新東京市。克勞斯身後應該加條電線才對）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  保鏢部隊和警衛機器人們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救出大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們敢對主人下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  戲份也到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒操縱小凪的那個影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛菊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好高…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有懼高症  還硬要逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣才像雛菊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這種時候就應該拜託伊澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咋就偏偏不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂啊…漂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  伊澄又和往常一樣地習慣性迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的「劇情需要」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真是的  又迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計可施了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個管家能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（實體劍突破GN-Field！）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  請回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  請您抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微鬧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪…颯先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經被各種動漫和遊戲用到快爛掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是依然王道的  人工呼吸橋段？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行  沒時間猶豫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去小颯會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯你個大白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪兒來的台詞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是個無人島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我很擅長野外求生的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜索隊到來之前  我不會讓大小姐吃苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…如果我能再坦率一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  大小姐的泳衣很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋  都這種時候了還說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對呢  不過請不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回不了宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會永遠保護大小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我不介意的  只要有你在就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是不是來得太早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  兩個人都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡也算是在宅邸內
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯再一次體會到了三千院家財力的龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.94,0:24:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方居然有海水浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露娜  就算是印度人也會嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  我可一點都不吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道夏露娜是從外星來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  請不要想到什麼就馬上說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.98,0:25:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500日元～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:06.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（入場費  500日元）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.25,0:25:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.81,0:25:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著這條路直走就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.73,0:25:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  能解釋一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雛  這個月的生活費有點吃緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把錢還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.93,0:25:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼姐姐你總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------------------
